      • getDefaultTokens

        public final List<HttpSessionToken> getDefaultTokens()
        Gets the default tokens.

        The list of default session tokens returned is read-only view of the internal default session tokens representation and any modifications will result in UnsupportedOperationException. No change should be done to the HttpSessionTokens contained in the list.

        Returns:
        the default tokens
